# ❌ DO NOT Use mingster.backbone

## Important Notice

**This project (mingster.com) does NOT have `mingster.backbone` configured and should NOT use it.**

## Why This Rule Exists

The `mingster.backbone` package is NOT available in this workspace because:

1. ❌ Not in `package.json` dependencies
2. ❌ Not configured in `tsconfig.json` paths
3. ❌ Package directory not accessible from this workspace
4. ❌ This is a standalone project with its own local components

## What to Use Instead

